- Fix SourceView key collisions in multi-context mode
- Clear WebSocket subscriptions when DataBrowser table empties
- Validate n2kChannelLabel request body types at boundary
- Clean up pgnDataInstances/pgnSourceKeys on source removal
- Dedupe sourceref migration when newRef already exists
- Add admin middleware to /multiSourcePaths endpoint
- Exclude priority badge from non-admin sidebar
- Fix stale contextOptions when vessel names arrive late
- Add REST API doc disclaimer for payload examples
- Add multi-bus regression test for instance conflicts
- Extract discovery timing magic numbers into constants
- Fix unsafe MouseEvent cast in keyboard handler
- Use SourcePolicy union type instead of loose string
- Type pipedProviders in nmea0183TalkerGroups
