Date: Thu, 16 Apr 2026 10:39:13 +1200
Subject: [PATCH 27/46] fix(ui): render Unit Preferences when authentication is
 disabled

The page only fetched unit preferences when loginStatus.status was
'loggedIn', which never happens on servers with security disabled
(authenticationRequired=false, status='notLoggedIn'). The fetch never
ran, unitPrefsLoaded stayed false, and the component rendered null.

Also trigger the fetch when authenticationRequired === false.
