From 52401ea86b67be2a657eabaa90e55cbba79e261f Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: dirkwa <dirkwahrtheit@gmail.com>
Date: Fri, 17 Apr 2026 10:48:33 +1200
Subject: [PATCH 40/46] refactor(ui+server): address CodeRabbit review findings

Real bugs:
- useSourceAliases: reject arrays in localStorage migration validation
- serverroutes: clone settings before write for /sourceAliases and
  /ignoredInstanceConflicts so failed writes do not corrupt in-memory
  state (matches /sourcePriorities pattern)
- SourceGroupHeader: keyboard accessibility (role/tabIndex/aria-expanded)
- SourceLabel: edit icon converted to <button> with aria-label
- n2k-discovery: only emit SOURCEALIASES after successful settings write
- deltacache: guard NaN in address comparison (canName-based keys)
- TimestampCell: reset animate state on pause to avoid stuck animation
- events: defensive {} fallback for MULTISOURCEPATHS payload
- Sidebar: defensive null guards on unconfiguredPriorityCount memo

Polish:
- SourceLabel: skip alias save when value unchanged
- WebSocketService: replace dynamic imports with statically-imported
  useStore (consistency, removes potential race ordering)
- UnitPreferencesSettings: drop unused loginStatus.username effect dep
- DataBrowser: rename callback param 'raw' (shadowed state) to
  'sourcesData' and add error logging
- SourcePriorities: log fetch errors instead of swallowing
- Sidebar: consistent isAdmin check; move inline <style> to CSS file
- GranularSubscriptionManager: simplify similarity check; always
  unsubscribe even when uniquePaths is empty
- SourceDiscovery: extract loadDeviceStatus helper, dedupe useEffect
- useSourceAliases: extract persistAliases helper; removeAlias
  delegates to setAlias
- sourceref-migration: use Set<string> for migrated tracking; do not
  count deltaCache cleanup as a config migration
- sourceLabels.ts: also skip 'label' key in buildSourceLabelMap
- config.ts: JSDoc and concrete type for sourceAliases
- MetaDataPage: remove dead form attributes

Test cleanup:
- sourcePolicy: close ws after assertions
- sourceref-migration: remove unused mock infrastructure
- deltacache: assert specific preferred source
- nmea0183TalkerGroups: rename misleading test description
