From 6c552f8e13a4fb11453a4ea2740b9942091b1d7e Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: dirkwa <dirkwahrtheit@gmail.com>
Date: Fri, 17 Apr 2026 14:10:02 +1200
Subject: [PATCH 41/46] fix(ui+server): Data Browser PGN search, filter toggle
 wiring, CR review
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

Features:
- Data Browser search now also matches against PGN number and NMEA0183
  sentence (e.g. typing 65017 finds all paths from PGN 65017).

Bug fixes:
- N2K connection filter Enabled toggle: synthetic checkbox event now
  carries .checked alongside .value, and handleProviderChange falls
  back to .value when .checked is undefined. Toggle state now persists
  across Apply.
- N2KFilters: coerce filtersEnabled to boolean in the checked prop so
  the toggle is always controlled (avoids uncontrolled warnings when
  filtersEnabled is undefined in settings).
- ProvidersConfiguration: tightened type narrowing in
  handleProviderChange — runtime check ('checked' in target) instead
  of unsafe type assertion.
- sourceLabels.ts: removed unreachable PGN 130823 from
  COMPOUND_KEY_PGNS (it is filtered earlier as proprietary).
- useSignalKData.ts + DataBrowser.tsx: guard vp.value for null /
  non-object before Object.keys to avoid potential TypeError on
  malformed deltas.
- SourcePriorities.tsx: aria-labels on Enable checkbox, move-up/down
  buttons, and converted both delete icons (path row + priority row)
  from clickable <FontAwesomeIcon> to <button> elements with proper
  aria-labels and keyboard support.
- SourceGroupHeader.tsx: aria-hidden on the decorative chevron
  (collapse state already conveyed via aria-expanded).
- GranularSubscriptionManager.startDiscovery: clear pending debounce
  timer to avoid stale resubscription firing after WebSocket reset.
- useSourceAliases.ts: also validate that all migrated alias values
  are strings before uploading to the server.
- nmea0183TalkerGroups.ts: exclude arrays from typeof === 'object'
  check on talkerGroups (same pattern as useSourceAliases).
